---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { site } from '../content/site';
import '../styles/tailwind.css';
---

<Base title="Terms of Service — Legacy Financial & Life" description="Terms of service for Legacy Financial & Life. Read about the terms governing your use of our website and services.">
  <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl flex items-center justify-between gap-4 px-4 py-3">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 min-w-0" aria-label="Legacy Financial & Life home">
        <img src={site.branding.logo} alt={site.branding.logoAlt} class="h-10 w-10 flex-shrink-0 object-contain" width="40" height="40" />
        <span class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900 hidden sm:inline truncate">{site.name}</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 transition-colors">
        &larr; Back to Home
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-10">Effective Date: June 26, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Agreement to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing or using the Legacy Financial &amp; Life website at legacyfinancial.app (the "Site"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Site.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Services</h2>
        <p>
          Legacy Financial &amp; Life ("we," "us," or "our") is a licensed insurance agency based in {site.cityState}. Through the Site, we provide information about our insurance and financial services, accept quote requests and inquiries, and facilitate communication between prospective clients and our licensed agents.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          The Site is not a substitute for professional financial or insurance advice. All insurance products and services described on the Site are subject to carrier terms, underwriting requirements, and applicable state regulations.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Communications Consent</h2>
        <p>
          By submitting a form on our Site, requesting a quote, or clicking a link in one of our emails, you consent to receive communications from Legacy Financial &amp; Life, including:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Phone calls and voicemails regarding your inquiry or application</li>
          <li>Text messages (SMS) with appointment confirmations, booking links, and service updates</li>
          <li>Emails related to your insurance needs, quote requests, or agent recruitment opportunities</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Message frequency varies. Message and data rates may apply. You may opt out of text messages at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong> to any message. For help, reply <strong>HELP</strong> or contact us at <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`} class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 underline">{site.email}</a>.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Some communications may be initiated or assisted by automated systems, including AI-powered tools. When an AI assistant contacts you by phone, it will identify itself as an automated assistant and will not represent itself as a human agent.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Agent Recruitment</h2>
        <p>
          We may contact licensed insurance professionals about agent recruitment opportunities. If you are a licensed agent and receive outreach from us, it is because your information is publicly available through state Department of Insurance records or professional databases. You may opt out of recruitment communications at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong> to any message, clicking the unsubscribe link in any email, or contacting us directly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">User Conduct</h2>
        <p>You agree not to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Use the Site for any unlawful purpose</li>
          <li>Submit false or misleading information through any form</li>
          <li>Attempt to interfere with or disrupt the Site's operation</li>
          <li>Scrape, harvest, or collect data from the Site without authorization</li>
          <li>Impersonate any person or entity in communications with us</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          All content on the Site — including text, graphics, logos, images, and software — is the property of Legacy Financial &amp; Life or its licensors and is protected by applicable copyright and trademark laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from Site content without our written permission.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p>
          The Site and its content are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, whether express or implied. We do not guarantee that the Site will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of harmful components. Insurance quotes and illustrations provided through the Site are estimates only and are subject to carrier underwriting and approval.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, Legacy Financial &amp; Life shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of the Site or services, including but not limited to loss of data, revenue, or business opportunity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>
          The Site may contain links to third-party websites, including carrier portals, scheduling services (such as Calendly), and training platforms. We are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or terms of those third-party sites.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Your use of the Site is also governed by our <a href="/privacy" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 underline">Privacy Policy</a>, which describes how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may update these Terms of Service from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. Your continued use of the Site after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms of Service are governed by the laws of the State of Georgia, without regard to conflict of law principles.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-none pl-0 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>{site.name}</strong></li>
          <li>Email: <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`} class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 underline">{site.email}</a></li>
          <li>Phone: <a href={`tel:${site.phone.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '')}`} class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 underline">{site.phone}</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-400 py-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 text-center text-sm space-y-2">
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} {site.name}. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>{site.footerNote}</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Base>
